ALTER TABLE [umbracoWebhookRequest] ADD CONSTRAINT [PK_umbracoWebhookRequest] PRIMARY KEY CLUSTERED ([id])

[updateDate] DATETIME NOT NULL CONSTRAINT [DF_umbracoLongRunningOperation_updateDate] DEFAULT (GETDATE()),
[expirationDate] DATETIME NOT NULL)
ALTER TABLE [umbracoLongRunningOperation] ADD CONSTRAINT [PK_umbracoLongRunningOperation] PRIMARY KEY CLUSTERED ([id])
